<p id="caption-attachment-246843" class="wp-caption-text">“Embroidered quilt with earthworms, cockchafer beetle larvae, dandelion plants, Brussels sprout plants, pe-tsaï cabbage plants, kohlrabi cabbage plants, striped shield bug, green bottle flies, cabbage white butterfly caterpillars, cauliflower cabbage plants, savoy cabbage plants, white-tailed bumblebee, cabbage white butterflies, ladybird beetle, red-tailed bumblebee, honey bee, sewing machine and overlocker machine” (2024), cotton and polyester thread on linen fabric, cotton batting, 194 x 248.5 centimeters</p>
</div>
<div id="attachment_246847" style="width: 1843px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-246847" class="wp-image-246847 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dewar-gicquel-8.jpg" alt="a wooden bas relief in oak of a knit sweater" width="1833" height="1920" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dewar-gicquel-8.jpg 1833w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dewar-gicquel-8-640x670.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dewar-gicquel-8-960x1006.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dewar-gicquel-8-1466x1536.jpg 1466w" sizes="(max-width: 1833px) 100vw, 1833px"></p>
<p id="caption-attachment-246847" class="wp-caption-text">“Oak relief with cable stitch pull-over” (2024), oak, 117 x 112 x 9 centimeters</p>
</div>
<div id="attachment_246866" style="width: 1527px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-246866" class="wp-image-246866 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dewar-gicquel-10.jpg" alt="an oak cabinet with eggplants and an abstracted human torso on top" width="1517" height="1920" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dewar-gicquel-10.jpg 1517w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dewar-gicquel-10-640x810.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dewar-gicquel-10-960x1215.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dewar-gicquel-10-1214x1536.jpg 1214w" sizes="(max-width: 1517px) 100vw, 1517px"></p>
<p id="caption-attachment-246866" class="wp-caption-text">“Oak cabinet with courgettes and body fragments” (2024), oak, 155 x 89 x 70 centimeters</p>
</div>
<div id="attachment_246842" style="width: 1930px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-246842" class="wp-image-246842 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dewar-gicquel-3.jpg" alt="a green quilt with a pattern of flowers, worms, plants, insects, and a clarinet" width="1920" height="1560" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dewar-gicquel-3.jpg 1920w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dewar-gicquel-3-640x520.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dewar-gicquel-3-960x780.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dewar-gicquel-3-1536x1248.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px"></p>
