										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div>
<div id="attachment_246827" style="width: 1930px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-246827" class="wp-image-246827 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-5.jpg" alt="a profile view of a carved wooden poodle sculpture" width="1920" height="1440" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-5.jpg 1920w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-5-640x480.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-5-960x720.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-5-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-5-285x214.jpg 285w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px"></p>
<p id="caption-attachment-246827" class="wp-caption-text">All images © Misato Sano, shared with permission</p>
</div>
<p>From pudgy pugs to a precisely groomed poodle to a deliriously happy Shiba Inu, <a href="https://sanomisato.com/works/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Misato Sano</a>’s waggish pups emerge from single blocks of wood. The artist (<a href="http://thisiscolossal.com/tags/misato-sano">previously</a>) chisels expectant eyes and goofy grins, revealing individual personalities that showcase each breed’s distinctive look and attitude.</p>
<p>Misato views our canine companions as mirrors of our own personalities, and she began making these sculptures as reflections of her own thoughts and emotions, from excitement to worry to longing. Each portrayal channels myriad ways dogs can be free and open in their expressions of devotion, passion, and play.</p>
<p>Her solo exhibition will open this October at <a href="https://cyg-morioka.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cyg Gallery</a> in Morioka City, Iwate, Japan. Find more on the artist’s <a href="https://sanomisato.com/works/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">website</a> and <a href="https://www.instagram.com/misato_sano/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-246824 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-8.jpeg" alt="a playful shiba inu dog carved out of wood" width="1422" height="1392" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-8.jpeg 1422w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-8-640x626.jpeg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-8-960x940.jpeg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 1422px) 100vw, 1422px"></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-246825 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-6.jpg" alt="a collection of five quirky wooden sculptures of dogs" width="1920" height="1440" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-6.jpg 1920w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-6-640x480.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-6-960x720.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-6-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-6-285x214.jpg 285w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px"></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-246826 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-7.jpg" alt="a carved wooden sculpture of a Shih Tzu in a woodworking studio" width="1440" height="1440" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-7.jpg 1440w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-7-640x640.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-7-960x960.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-7-150x150.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px">  <img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-246828 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-3.jpg" alt="a wooden sculpture of an abstracted white dog with large paws" width="1305" height="1265" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-3.jpg 1305w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-3-640x620.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-3-960x931.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 1305px) 100vw, 1305px"></p>
